[normal]Dr Bennett[bold]: 
[normal]There were a few questions in there.
[normal]Dr Wollaston:[bold] 
[normal]I know.
[normal]Valerie [bold]Vaz[bold]:[bold] 
[normal]It was a speech, Sarah.
[normal]Dr Wollaston:[bold] 
[normal]It was a speech. I am sorry about that.
[normal]Dr Bennett[bold]: 
[normal]Fundamentally, it is all about what is going to drive improvements for patients. The competition is only there on the assumption that it will improve the quality of care for patients. But, as I say, the challenge is really
[normal],
[normal] 
[normal]“
